snippet.description:
All Proceeds Go to The Red Cross and The Hurricane Harvey Relief Fund! Links Below:
The Red Cross ►► https://goo.gl/Ex8KNk
Hurricane Harvey Relief Fund ►► https://goo.gl/Jw3Z8Q

Today's Stream is Dedicated to Dominic Saldivar.

After the destruction and floods caused by Hurricane Harvey, we decided the Theorist Community should do its best to help out. One good way to do this is by donating to help catastrophe relief efforts. So today we will have Super Chat enabled in order to raise money for this cause. 100% of our Super Chat Proceeds will go to help fund relief efforts working to save lives and rebuild infrastructure in Texas. For this Special Stream, we're playing UNDERTALE since we've been asked to play it more than any other game on GTLive. Join us for this special charity event!

Watch MORE on the GTLive Channel! ►► http://bit.ly/1LkSBnz 
USE: #GTLIVE and @matpatgt to send us comments & questions!
